{"tid":257531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文武雙全] 旺角樓上書店職員當街怒斬金融經紀！","createTime":"2017-05-25T10:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T16:18:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e24e6e36386e5944a93e1c37a2eff24697390e8a","tid":257531,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170525/56740195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170525%2F56740195&d=KBvGWA0y16EJK01kwjhrPC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=661ff5b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170525%2F56740195&h=e211ac53\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170525/56740195</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170525/large/1495694638_53ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170525%2Flarge%2F1495694638_53ba.jpg&h=bd164332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【15：43更新】新增影片<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌於今年1月在北角油街當街斬傷男經紀的刀手落網。一名任職金融業的經紀，當日早上行經北角公司附近街頭，遭襲擊受傷，刀手逞兇後逃去無蹤(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jCTsqe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jCTsqe&d=KBvGWA0y16EJK01kwjhrPC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=64fb1508\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jCTsqe</a>) 男子，據悉對方為一名書店職員。下午2時許，探員將他押到旺角奶路臣街一樓上書店蒐證。<br />\n<br />\n事發於今年1月16日，26歲姓侯事主途經北角油街及電器道交界，遭一名年約30歲男子持牛肉刀伏擊，侯手及背部中刀血流如注跌倒路旁，一名民安隊女隊員途經立即上前施救，傷者事後由救護車送院治理。"},{"pid":"35bf217bb541bd7da1da646296277dcf7cadb86a","tid":257531,"uid":102056,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44fb4bc09d35db6482089b7036a274f400c3e521","tid":257531,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依d仆街金融狗，斬柒佢就啱撚晒啦，洗撚救鳩佢咩<b